			      <div type="translation" xml:lang="eng">
				        <p>Memorial pillar of Sivadāsa of the Nārada gotra, son of the
					(...) masters, who died (lit. went to the heavens, <foreign xml:lang="san-Latn">svargagata</foreign>) in battle, (on the occasion of) a cattle raid.</p>
